data.text:
Below is the total number of games played in Europe by Rangers FC. Includes games played in qualifying rounds and includes all UEFA competitions as well as Fairs Cup and European Super Cup final in 1972 which is considered unofficial.

Total Games – 380

Wins – 162

Draw – 98

Lost – 120

Goals Scored – 576

Goals Conceded – 447

Best Finish by Competition

UEFA Champions League/European Cup – Semi Final

UEFA Europa League/UEFA Cup – Runner Up

UEFA Cup Winners Cup – Winners (1972)

European Super Cup – Runners Up

Fairs Cup – Semi Final

UEFA Conference League – N/A
